{"tid":822955,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯：我要練12碼！","createTime":"2018-09-16T14:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T14:44:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3abdc5382009d297317befd16c5ea0edfd922516","tid":822955,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JprAvwSNN9sYnN4iDHPv8eI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=fc420a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】百尺竿頭難進一步？不一定！球王美斯就印證了他都有不足的地方，更銳意要改善自己。<br />\n<br />\n30歲的美斯（Lionel Messi）球技了得是世所公認，不過原來球王亦有弱點。數據顯示美斯較弱的一環原來是12碼，上季他為球隊及國家隊上陣的比賽當中共射失8個12碼，令他球員生涯中失12碼的數字增至24個。<br />\n<br />\n美斯接受電台《Catalunya Radio》訪問時承認自己需要改善這個弱點：「我知道我在12碼下工夫，但這是知易行難。在訓練場上練12碼與比賽中主射是截然不同的。當然12碼這門學問中，龍門都有很多事要做，不過他們只要猜中了就有機會救到球。無論如何，我需要在12碼中表現得更好才行。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"e2a222d15fc85a3937e5d293879095dd01abe53e","tid":822955,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/abf3ab8920248eaf049319c9dca1bcb0/tenor.gif?itemid=5626112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fabf3ab8920248eaf049319c9dca1bcb0%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D5626112&h=8a9495c0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}